Class ResourceModelCaches

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.neba.core.resourcemodels.caching.ResourceModelCaches

  • @Service
public class ResourceModelCaches
extends Object
    Represents all currently registered resource model cache services.
    Thread-safety must be provided by the underlying caches.
    Author:
    Olaf Otto
